      <title>Cellnex 以 8.03 亿欧元出售子公司，暗示将回购股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/cellnex-sells-unit-for-803-million-signals-share-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙塔台运营商 Cellnex Telecom SA 已同意以 8.03 亿欧元（8.77 亿美元）的企业价值将其奥地利业务出售给由 Vauban Infrastructure Partners、EDF Invest 和 MEAG 组成的投资者财团，目前该财团正努力削减债务并退出较小的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/cellnex-sells-unit-for-803-million-signals-share-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 11:39:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
